<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='774000' id='t-774000'>There were people at my table who thought it was, you know, fantastic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='776000' id='t-776000'>There were some people who were a little less impressed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='780000' id='t-780000'>And I wasn't that impressed.</span>
